plot: Alex Hitchens is &"The Date Doctor.&" He helps men to land dates. Sara is a gossip columnist for a New York City tabloid. Both are very guarded around the opposite sex. Despite their natures, Alex and Sara begin a relationship. Complications ensue when Sara's latest scoop happens to be one of Alex's clients.   Written by  Ken Miller
title: Hitch, especialista en ligues
